    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thousands of years ago, humanity built colossal war machines to stop the apocalypse. Now they just use them for <strong>dance battles</strong>!  <br>  <br>Using your own music or the built-in soundtrack, groove your way across a rich world, assemble the perfect mecha crew, and rise from humble beginnings to ultimate stardom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/4f56c41ff203a3fb1e1f09bcfabe60aa.poster.avif?t=1770157748\" aria-label=\"Dance Dance Mecha! Challenge other pilots to intense dance-offs on a massive scale. \" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/4f56c41ff203a3fb1e1f09bcfabe60aa.webm?t=1770157748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/4f56c41ff203a3fb1e1f09bcfabe60aa.mp4?t=1770157748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/a6b3a80e702fc396a17d8036dd75a4da.poster.avif?t=1770157748\" aria-label=\"RPG Rhythm Battles. Each mech has a unique kit and special mechanics. Choose the best move for each note to defeat your opponent.\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/a6b3a80e702fc396a17d8036dd75a4da.webm?t=1770157748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/a6b3a80e702fc396a17d8036dd75a4da.mp4?t=1770157748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/8f7af4e5c67b12cd75299488bc2f4e5b.poster.avif?t=1770157748\" aria-label=\"A Pilot&#039;s Journey. Make friends and challenge rivals as you compete for the championship trophy. \" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/8f7af4e5c67b12cd75299488bc2f4e5b.webm?t=1770157748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/8f7af4e5c67b12cd75299488bc2f4e5b.mp4?t=1770157748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/2f50a55b5f493e589f5ec444a47117bb.poster.avif?t=1770157748\" aria-label=\"Turn Up The Volume. Groove to the awesome built-in soundtrack or bring your own MP3s.\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/2f50a55b5f493e589f5ec444a47117bb.webm?t=1770157748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/2f50a55b5f493e589f5ec444a47117bb.mp4?t=1770157748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/2fe6b1c6b77f565b161431eb20999ccb.poster.avif?t=1770157748\" aria-label=\"Gigantic Adventure. Battle from coast to coast and uncover the secrets behind the steel dance.\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/2fe6b1c6b77f565b161431eb20999ccb.webm?t=1770157748\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1858950/extras/2fe6b1c6b77f565b161431eb20999ccb.mp4?t=1770157748\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Additional Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Collect and Upgrade:</strong> Level up your mechs, equip them with mods, and pair them with different combinations of backup dancers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Gameplay Kits: </strong>Each mech has its own set of abilities, mechanics, and resources. A simple starter mech builds and spends energy, while later mechs have you maintaining an army of drones or swapping between cards in a mini deck-builder.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Flexible Rhythm Combat: </strong><i>Steel Century Groove</i> doesn't demand a specific button press for each note. Instead, pick from your mech's kit of battle abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Playing the Metronome:</strong> Challenge yourself against interesting melodies, even when playing with your own music. You’ll never just be endlessly tapping out the beat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No Accessories Required:</strong> Built from the start for gamepad or mouse &amp; keyboard.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Streamer Mode On:</strong> Enable Streamer Mode and the game will play only exclusive, original music that won't trigger any copyright claims on YouTube, Twitch, etc.<strong> </strong></p></li></ul>",
